# ============================================================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# ============================================================
# PRISMA
# ============================================================
# Generated client (di-generate ulang saat build)
# node_modules/.prisma sudah ter-cover di node_modules/

